intent.user_query: What is the sales trend over the last quarter?

phases.goal: Execute SQL query on fitness_db to retrieve the sales trend over the last quarter: SELECT SaleDate, SUM(TotalAmount) FROM fitness_db.Sales WHERE SaleDate >= CURRENT_DATE - INTERVAL '3' MONTH GROUP BY SaleDate ORDER BY SaleDate;

arguments.sql: SELECT SaleDate, SUM(TotalAmount) FROM fitness_db.Sales WHERE SaleDate >= CURRENT_DATE - INTERVAL '3' MONTH GROUP BY SaleDate ORDER BY SaleDate;

phases.goal: Generate the final report based on the query results.
